string.text:
1) "Light indicator" displays amount of light on player. 

 2) "NPC vision" displays how NPC (with highest vision value on you) see player: 
 - White icon: NPC in normal state and does not see player; 
 - Yellow icon: NPC is in combat/danger (has boosted vision parameters) and does not see player; 
 - Red icon: NPC see player.
